This is a port of comet-based chat application found at:

  https://github.com/miyagawa/Tatsumaki/tree/master/eg/chat

It was originally written for:

  - Perl5 http://www.perl.org/
  - Tatsumaki http://github.com/miyagawa/Tatsumaki
  - Twiggy http://github.com/miyagawa/Twiggy
  - jquery-ev https://github.com/beppu/jquery-ev
  - DUI Stream https://github.com/digg/stream

and now uses:

  - node.js http://nodejs.org/
  - express.js http://expressjs.com/
  - CoffeeScript http://jashkenas.github.com/coffee-script/
  - CoffeeKup https://github.com/mauricemach/coffeekup
  - socket.io http://socket.io/

